channel.title: CVE Feed for Jenkins project -- Jenkins Custom Checkbox Parameter Plugin
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Jenkins project -- Jenkins Custom Checkbox Parameter Plugin

item.title: CVE-2022-25189|2024-08-03T04:36:05.782Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20custom%20checkbox%20parameter%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Custom Checkbox Parameter Plugin 1.1 and earlier does not escape parameter names of custom checkbox parameters, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers with Item/Configure permission.

item.title: CVE-2022-43425|2024-08-03T13:32:58.677Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20custom%20checkbox%20parameter%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Custom Checkbox Parameter Plugin 1.4 and earlier does not escape the name and description of Custom Checkbox Parameter parameters on views displaying parameters, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers with Item/Configure permission.
